Деревянная гелевая ручка (5 шт.)

2990 руб.
Идеальный дизайн: Stainless steel body made of superior copper. Having perfect balance and appropriate weight, and feels comfortable to your hand. Cap clips on and off precisely and firmly with a nice snap.We recommend using ЛазерПеккер LP2/4 for DIY creative laser engraving.

Высочайшее качество письма: Super-smooth writing experience, no leakage, no smudging. Ink dries quickly and never fades.Larger-capacity ink tube for a long life span.

Ультра роскошный внешний вид: Sophisticated brushed stainless
steel body, gleaming 23 karat golden trim and clip makes a good sense of view and touch. Feeling substantial and premium when writing.

Замечательный вариант подарка: Each pen is placed in a perfect box, This is the perfect gift for parents, teachers, friends and classmates ,Also, you can buy one to reward yourself!

Время доставки: 7-30 Business Day.
